<bibRefCitation author="Gullan" box="[339,633,398,424]" pageId="33" pageNumber="38" refString="Gullan, P. J. &amp; Sjaarda, A. W. (2001) Trans-Tasman Platycoelostoma Morrison (Hemiptera: Coccoidea: Margarodidae) on endemic Cupressaceae, and the phylogenetic history of margarodids. Systematic Entomology, 26, 257 - 278." type="journal article" year="2001">
