)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Morales" box="[645,826,398,424]" pageId="33" pageNumber="38" refString="Morales, C. F. (1991) Margarodidae (Insecta: Hemiptera). Fauna of New Zealand, 21, 1 - 123" type="journal article" year="1991">
