<bibRefCitation author="Morrison" box="[883,1227,398,424]" pageId="33" pageNumber="38" refString="Morrison, H. &amp; Morrison, E. R. (1923) The scale insects of the subfamilies Monophlebinae and Margarodinae treated by Maskell. Proceedings of the United States National Museum (Washington), 62, 1 - 47." type="journal article" year="1923">
